item.title: Drill deal - sbr (ft. ITJ) [Hip-hop, trap, drill]
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
I like the art lol, kudos for not only making an interesting thing to look at but also just doing one at all (so many folks don’t).

I’m not super big on trap, or whatever, but, I dig the vibe. You’ve got this middle eastern thing going on which is cool, something different. My only suggestion (if you’re open to it, maybe something to keep in mind for next time) is that the siren volume that comes in a couple times seems a tad loud. But otherwise everything seems to fit well, and you’ve cut it at a good length. Good job
